===It's another new day today, (Trailblazer).===
{{Messages|text=
:'''Welt:''' It's another new day today, (Trailblazer).
:'''Welt:''' When we step on the Express and follow in the footsteps of the Nameless, it means that we will become accustomed to things that are not of the ordinary.
:'''Welt:''' You will push beyond your limits without even realizing it.
:'''Welt:''' (Trailblazer), have you experienced anything like that before?
:{Choice} I have suddenly started receiving a huge volume of messages.
::'''(Trailblazer):''' Indeed, I have suddenly started receiving a huge volume of messages
::'''Welt:''' Messages represent the connection between people.
::'''Welt:''' If you receive messages every day, it means that the connection between you and others has deepened during your Trailblaze journey.
::'''Welt:''' But connections also need to be maintained. Take care to manage your time wisely.
:{Choice} I have suddenly started receiving many new assignments.
::'''(Trailblazer):''' Indeed, I have suddenly started receiving many new assignments
::'''Welt:''' You can't count yourself as worthy of the Nameless if you can't handle several assignments at the same time.
::'''Welt:''' Plan your route efficiently so that you won't run around the same circle twice. Otherwise, you're just doing extra work.
::'''Welt:''' Before you know it, you'll have already developed the muscle memory for it.
;(All choices lead to the following options)
:{Choice} Sounds like you're a seasoned veteran
::'''(Trailblazer):''' Sounds like you're a seasoned veteran, Mr. Yang!
::'''Welt:''' The experience of the Nameless is but a lesson of sweat and blood.
::'''Welt:''' [[File:Sticker PPG 07 Pom-Pom 05.png|80px|&lbrack;Okay&rbrack;]]
:{Choice} Such is the price of following Trailblaze
::'''(Trailblazer):''' If this is the price of following Trailblaze, I'm willing to pay it!
::'''Welt:''' To have attained such enlightenment at such a young age.
::'''Welt:''' [[File:Sticker PPG 07 Pom-Pom 06.png|80px|&lbrack;Thumbs Up&rbrack;]]
}}
