===(Trailblazer), I just got...===
{{Messages|text=
:'''Welt:''' (Trailblazer), I just got a great idea!
:'''Welt:''' We can make an animation based on the Express!
:{Choice} [Shocked]
::'''(Trailblazer):''' [[File:Sticker PPG 07 Pom-Pom 08.png|80px|&lbrack;Shocked&rbrack;]]
:{Choice} [Thumbs Up]
::'''(Trailblazer):''' [[File:Sticker PPG 07 Pom-Pom 06.png|80px|&lbrack;Thumbs Up&rbrack;]]
:{Choice} [Decline]
::'''(Trailblazer):''' [[File:Sticker PPG 07 Pom-Pom 04.png|80px|&lbrack;Decline&rbrack;]]
::'''Welt:''' Hear me out on this one.
:'''Welt:''' Of course, the story would take place in the distant past.
:'''Welt:''' And for obvious, practical reasons, we will most likely need to modify most of the plot in the end... but that's just an afterthought.
:'''Welt:''' I've been out of the industry for a long time now, and frankly, I'm especially interested in hearing what you young people think.
:'''Welt:''' For example, what would you find most compelling in such a story?
:{Choice} An adventure with ups and downs
::'''(Trailblazer):''' It should be an adventure with ups and downs
::'''Welt:''' Unique settings and a collision of destinies &mdash; can't do without either of those.
:{Choice} A thrilling, relentless battle
::'''(Trailblazer):''' It should be a thrilling, relentless battle
::'''Welt:''' Companions who have each other's backs, and powerful enemies &mdash; can't do without either of those.
:{Choice} I want to see the protagonist fully upgrade their equipment
::'''(Trailblazer):''' In truth, I just want to see the protagonist fully upgrade their equipment
::'''Welt:''' That is, the protagonist keeps getting upgrades and getting stronger, right?
:'''Welt:''' Next question: When do you think this story should end?
:{Choice} I hope it never ends
::'''(Trailblazer):''' I hope it never ends
::'''Welt:''' Maybe you could serialize it? That sort of thing has been done before.
:{Choice} When everyone's wishes come true
::'''(Trailblazer):''' When everyone's wishes come true
::'''Welt:''' After reaching a satisfying conclusion... stories like that have been told before in animation.
:{Choice} When everyone's equipment is fully upgraded
::'''(Trailblazer):''' When everyone's equipment is fully upgraded
::'''Welt:''' If the story is forced to continue after everyone's equipment has been fully upgraded, the battles may become unbalanced.
:'''Welt:''' I'm actually really glad that you see our journey that way.
:'''Welt:''' Looks like I'll have to make this dream come true after my next retirement...
:'''Welt:''' (Trailblazer), wait until that time comes, and then we'll have a nice chat again.
}}
